{"content": "I need to multiply 41a \u00d7 951 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 41a (base 11) to base 10**\n- 41a = 4\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 10\u00d711\u2070\n- = 4\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 10\u00d71\n- = 484 + 11 + 10\n- = 505\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 951 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 951 = 9\u00d711\u00b2 + 5\u00d711\u00b9 + 1\u00d711\u2070\n- = 9\u00d7121 + 5\u00d711 + 1\u00d71\n- = 1089 + 55 + 1\n- = 1145\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 505 \u00d7 1145 = 578,225\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 578,225 back to base 11**\n- 578,225 \u00f7 11 = 52,565 R 0\n- 52,565 \u00f7 11 = 4,778 R 7\n- 4,778 \u00f7 11 = 434 R 4\n- 434 \u00f7 11 = 39 R 5\n- 39 \u00f7 11 = 3 R 6\n- 3 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 3\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 365470\n\n365470", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 386}